      description: "记录一下我为什么想留一个更安静、更能自己控制的小站。",
      date: "2026-05-23",
      categories: ["personal", "writing"],
      tags: ["vue", "typescript", "ssg", "i18n", "content-system"],
      featured: true,
      order: 1,
      path: "/zh/posts/building-this-site/",
